<HEAD>Stork To Visit Jets' No. 99 and Sly's Ex</HEAD>
<DATELINE>NEW YORK (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Pro football's Mark Gastineau and athletic
actress Brigitte Nielsen are expecting a baby, Gastineau says.
   The New York Jets' defensive lineman, checking into his team's
