``happier than she has ever been about anything.''
   Gastineau was once the beefy star of the Jets' ``sack
exchange,'' but his performance has slumped the last two seasons.
He and Nielsen met while working out at a San Diego health club
during Super Bowl week.
   Nielsen, a statuesque blond who has appeared in such adventure
films as ``Red Sonia,'' was in Rome on Tuesday to start work on a
new movie, ``Domino.''
