   April 29
   The Mitchell (S.D.) Daily Republic on coach Bob Knight:
   Indiana basketball coach Bob Knight may be able to come up with
great game strategies. But his effort at making analogies leaves us
wondering if the locker room smell of sweatsocks is beginning to
take its toll.
   On (an) NBC television special dealing with stress,
