new takeover proposal for the company with a deal that combine cash
and securities.
   The NYSE's composite index of all its listed common stocks
dropped .44 to 148.13. On the American Stock Exchange, the market
value index was up .11 at 303.33.
   Volume on the Big Board came to 96.85 million shares with two
hours to go.
