13}. The company said a management group led by its chairman and
president made a buyout proposal at $13.50 a share.
   Allegis gained 5\ to 90. A union representing pilots at the
company's United Airlines raised the possibility of a $110-a-share
cash merger offer if the union prevails in a court action filed
last week.
